		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm slowly getting into creating some of the assets for my game (8k CHR-ROM only) and I'd like to get some criticism and ideas on how to improve myself. Generally I practice with art I receive/commission or find on the internet by using them as a base for &quot;pixelization&quot; as far as the mugshot and the sprite go. The backgrounds do not use any kind of base image except for certain terrain objects (like the palm trees).<br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
