	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On a TV, the top bar might be cut off, you might as well drop that down 1, for balance also.<br /><br />The lava at the bottom is nice. It looks like a river. It would be nice if it was scrolling independent of the top.<br /><br />On the short volcano, the straight line on the orange is a little unnatural.<br /><br />The rocks look like they are objects you can bump into. Not sure what your plan is there.<br /><br />My main concern, altogether, is...how is a small cat a shmup? Laser cats (old SNL skit)?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


